              <content>
                <p>This section makes provision for Northern Ireland similar to that made by section 2. In this case the power to make regulations is conferred on the Department for Communities in Northern Ireland.</p>
              </content>
            </paragraph>
            <level>
              <content>
                <p>Section 54: Qualifying schemes</p>
              </content>
            </level>
            <paragraph>
              <num>255 </num>
              <content>
